beer.beer_description: The postman delivers! He is bringing a sanitised hop filled package at a socially acceptable distance for a non-contact delivery. This beer is a salute to the Postie’s that brought us all delicious beers through lockdown. The aroma is loaded with tropical fruit and citrus, it’s packaged up with a medium body of bready, biscuit flavours and delivers a dry finish. The tropical, mango and citrus flavours will be stamped all over your tastebuds.
